Description: ONVIF event recorder for UniFi Protect
 Subscribes to ONVIF cameras, parses their motion/smart-detect events, and
 records detection intervals into the UniFi Protect PostgreSQL database so
 third-party cameras appear alongside first-party ones in the Protect UI.
 .
 Also polls first-party motion events, runs NanoDet-M object detection on
 thumbnails, and triggers Protect automations (alarm sounds, recording rules)
 on smart-detect hits.

